abstract: Los Angeles police investigator suspect 14 teenagers of sexual assault against two Venice High School students; nine have been arrested and officers are searching for remaining five.
lead_paragraph: Fourteen teenagers are under investigation for a series of sexual assaults against two students at a Los Angeles high school, the police said Friday.
